# Description
# -----------
# Docker Compose file for deploying MSIMPL microservices inside the
# Docker environment.
#
# Infrastructure components (Kafka, Kafka UI, etc.) must already be
# running before starting these application containers.
#
# Notes
# -----
# 1. PostgreSQL runs on the Windows host.
#
# 2. All services connect to PostgreSQL using:
#
#       host.docker.internal
#
# 3. All services communicate with Kafka using:
#
#       kafka:9092
#
# 4. All services communicate over the shared Docker network:
#
#       infra_msimpl-network
#
# =============================================================================

